title: Devante Parker Traded; Cuál Es Tu Fantasía: El Regreso
itunes:title: Devante Parker Traded; Cuál Es Tu Fantasía: El Regreso
description:
A room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Colleen Wolfe bring you all the latest news around the league. The Patriots traded for Devante Parker, Xavien Howard received a new contract, Frank Gore is retiring with the Niners, Colin Kaepernick worked out during Michigan's spring game, and the Browns are expected to trade Baker Mayfield before the draft. Plus, the long-awaited return of “Cuál Es Tu Fantasía?”

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
